compute_session_info <- function(df_temp, timezone_lable) {
  df_temp <- df_temp %>% 
    arrange(classid, timestamp) %>% 
    group_by(classid) %>%
    mutate(
      event_timestamp = with_tz(ymd_hms(timestamp, tz='UTC'), tzone = timezone_lable), 
      event_timestamp_year = year(event_timestamp),
      event_timestamp_month = month(event_timestamp),
      event_timestamp_day = day(event_timestamp),
      event_timestamp_hour = hour(event_timestamp),
      next_event_timestamp = lead(event_timestamp),
      time_diff = round(as.numeric(difftime(next_event_timestamp, event_timestamp, units="mins")),3),
      time_diff = coalesce(time_diff, 0.001)) %>% 
    mutate(session_break_7_5 = if_else(time_diff > (7.5), 1, 0), 
           class_session_id_7_5 = paste0("class_session_", cumsum(lag(session_break_7_5, default = 0)))) %>% 
    ungroup()
  
  
  df_class_session_info <- df_temp %>% 
    group_by(state, sch_id, tea_id, classid,  class_session_id_7_5) %>% 
    summarise(class_session_length = round(as.numeric(difftime(max(event_timestamp), min(event_timestamp), units="mins")),3),
              class_session_size = n_distinct(studyStudentID),
              class_session_start_hour = min(event_timestamp_hour),
              class_session_end_hour = max(event_timestamp_hour),
              class_session_start_time = min(event_timestamp), 
              class_session_end_time = max(event_timestamp),
              counting = n(),
              class_session_type = case_when(class_session_start_hour >= 7 & class_session_end_hour <= 15 & class_session_size < 5 ~ "at school independent work",
                                             class_session_start_hour >= 7 & class_session_end_hour <= 15 & class_session_size >= 5 ~ "classwork",
                                             TRUE~"homework 1"))  
  
  df_student_session_info <- df_temp %>% 
    arrange(state, sch_id, tea_id, classid, class_session_id_7_5, studyStudentID, timestamp) %>% 
    group_by(state, sch_id, tea_id, classid, class_session_id_7_5, studyStudentID, grade, locale, score_1, score_2) %>% 
    mutate(student_next_timestamp = lead(event_timestamp), 
           student_time_diff = round(as.numeric(difftime(student_next_timestamp, event_timestamp, units="mins")),3), 
           student_time_diff = coalesce(time_diff, 0.001)) %>% 
    summarise(tx_count = n(), 
              student_session_length = round(as.numeric(difftime(max(event_timestamp), min(event_timestamp), units="mins")),3),
              idle_time_gt_120 = sum(ifelse(student_time_diff > 1.05 & student_time_diff < 7.5, student_time_diff, 0)),
              student_session_start_time = min(event_timestamp), 
              student_session_end_time = max(event_timestamp), 
              student_session_start_year = min(event_timestamp_year),
              student_session_start_month = min(event_timestamp_month),
              student_session_start_day = min(event_timestamp_day))
    
  
  intersect(colnames(df_student_session_info), colnames(df_class_session_info))
  
  df_session_merged = left_join(df_class_session_info, df_student_session_info, by=c("state", "classid", "tea_id", "sch_id", "class_session_id_7_5"))
  
  df_session_merged <- df_session_merged %>% 
    mutate(student_delayed_start = round(as.numeric(difftime(student_session_start_time, class_session_start_time, units="mins")), 3),
           student_early_stop = round(as.numeric(difftime(class_session_end_time, student_session_end_time, units="mins")), 3)) %>% 
    group_by(classid, class_session_id_7_5) %>% 
    mutate(
      relative_student_delayed_start = as.numeric(scale(student_delayed_start)), 
      relative_student_session_length = as.numeric(scale(student_session_length)), 
      relative_student_early_stop = as.numeric(scale(student_early_stop)), 
      relative_idle_time_gt_120 = as.numeric(scale(idle_time_gt_120)))
  return(df_session_merged)
}

Measuers from the paper

  1. delayed start (raw and realtive)
  2. session length (raw and realtive)
  3. early stop (raw and relative)
  4. idle time (raw and realtive)
  5. total time on task (mins)
  6. usage time ratio (raw and realtive)
  7. attendance
  8. gaming tendency
